snippet.title: Mario & Luigi: Brothership – Announcement Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The bond between brothers has never been stronger! Set sail for an island-hopping adventure with the Mario Bros. in Mario & Luigi: Brothership!

Launching November 7th 2024 on Nintendo Switch. Pre-order now: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/mario-and-luigi-brothership-switch/?utm_source=SW-AA&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=N1138-01&utm_id=N1138-01
